home.main.title:

Choose your closest pick up location, Print n' Go
home.main.description:
Don't have access to a working printer or running out of ink? We got you covered! Print n' go is the quickest, closest, and most convenient way to print documents out there!

We are privacy oriented and provide a secure payment system so you never need coins for printing documents again!
home.whyPrintnGo.title: Why Print n' Go?
home.howItWorks.title: How It Works?
home.howItWorks.step3: Make a secure payment and get an access code
home.howItWorks.step4: Provide the access code at the counter and gather your documents
home.quickest.title: The quickest process and simplest way for printing documents
home.quickest.description:
We're close to you, we cut down your travel time.

No need to carry around your USB key any longer. Just upload, arrive and print.

Once your documents are uploaded, you will no longer need a computer for completing the printing. Our partners, at the pick up locations, will do the printing for you.
home.closest.title: We are the closest printing service near you
home.closest.description: How? Our pick up locations are your favourite convenient stores, cafes, pharmacies and any kind of shop that has a printing machine.
home.privacyOriented.title: We are privacy oriented
home.privacyOriented.description: Your privacy is the most important for us. We will provide you with an access code so that only you can access and trigger the print of your documents.
home.securePayment.title: No need to have coins anymore
home.securePayment.description: Simply pay online before hand with our secure payment system.
home.storeDocument.title: We store your documents so you can print them quicker in the future.
home.storeDocument.description:
Once you have uploaded your documents once, we will save them on your account so that you can print them even quicker in the future.

And if you want to be even quicker, top up your wallet with our top up deals and skip the need of providing your card details each time.
home.bestValue.title: Best value
home.bestValue.description: Our service is awesome, it doesn't mean it should be more expensive! We provide you with the best printing service at the best price.
home.contact.title: We love hearing from you
home.contact.description: Having questions, want to give a feedback or just say hello? You can contact us anytime at contact@printngo.ca
